OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with sunny spells at first
OL,6,Fthen cloud and rain in the southwest
OL,7,Fsoon spreads northeast becoming heavy
OL,8,Fat times. This rain will clear to
OL,9,Fsunny spells and the odd shower in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright or clear spells with
OL,13,Fthe occasional shower in the south
OL,14,Fbecoming cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fsome heavy, towards the morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy rain becoming drier
OL,19,Fwith bright spells towards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
